# Persib Manager 2026 🏆

Game football manager berbasis web — pimpin Maung Bandung merajai BRI Super League 2025/26!

## Cara Main Lokal

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Buka http://localhost:3000

## Deploy ke Vercel

1. Push ke GitHub
2. Import di vercel.com
3. Deploy otomatis ✅

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 15
- React 19
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS v4
- Framer Motion
